OL,3,CAustralian PM supports removing Andrew
OL,4,Cfrom royal line of succession
OL,6,FAustralia's Prime Minister Anthony
OL,7,FAlbanese has written to Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer to say his government would
OL,9,Fagree to "any proposal" to remove
OL,10,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor from the
OL,11,Fline of succession.
OL,13,FHe said: "In light of recent events
OL,14,Fconcerning Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor,
OL,15,FI am writing to confirm that my
OL,16,Fgovernment would agree to any proposal
OL,17,Fto remove him from the line of royal
OL,18,Fsuccession.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@WO]
