OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771952662
OL,3,CAustralian PM supports removing Andrew
OL,4,Cfrom royal line of succession
OL,6,F"I agree with His Majesty that the law
OL,7,Fmust now take its full course and
OL,8,Fthere must be a full, fair and proper
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"These are grave allegations and
OL,12,FAustralians take them seriously."
OL,14,FThe former prince was arrested on
OL,15,FThursday on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,16,Fpublic office after being accused of
OL,17,Fsharing sensitive information with
OL,18,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein
OL,19,Fwhile serving as the UK's trade envoy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
