CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771952662
OL,3,CAustralian PM supports removing Andrew
OL,4,Cfrom royal line of succession
OL,6,FAndrew spent 11 hours in custody on
OL,7,Fhis 66th birthday while officers
OL,8,Fsearched his home on the Sandringham
OL,9,FEstate in Norfolk. He was released
OL,10,Funder investigation.
OL,12,FAlthough Andrew was stripped of his
OL,13,Fremaining royal titles by his brother,
OL,14,FKing Charles III, in December, he
OL,15,Fcurrently remains eighth in line to
OL,16,Fthe throne.
OL,18,FStarmer's government will consider
OL,19,Fintroducing legislation to remove this
OL,20,Fright once police have concluded their
OL,21,Finvestigation into Andrew.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
