OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771952662
OL,3,CAustralian PM supports removing Andrew
OL,4,Cfrom royal line of succession
OL,6,FAny changes to the line of succession
OL,7,Fwould require the agreement of other
OL,8,Fcountries that share the UK monarch,
OL,9,Fincluding Australia, Canada and
OL,10,FJamaica.
OL,12,FAustralia's PM is the first leader of
OL,13,Fa Commonwealth country to publicly
OL,14,Fback removing Andrew from being in
OL,15,Fline to the throne.
OL,17,FWhen asked about a letter the letter
OL,18,Ffrom Albanese, Starmer's official
OL,19,Fspokesman said: "The government has
OL,20,Freceived the letter.
OL,26,@{D@QOU
