OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771952662
OL,3,CAustralian PM supports removing Andrew
OL,4,Cfrom royal line of succession
OL,6,F"We are considering whether further
OL,7,Fsteps are required in relation to
OL,8,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor, and we are
OL,9,Fnot ruling anything out.
OL,11,F"But given the ongoing police
OL,12,Finvestigation, it would not be
OL,13,Fappropriate for the Government to
OL,14,Fcomment further at this stage."
OL,16,FDowning Street said it was up to
OL,17,FParliament whether a special committee
OL,18,Fshould investigate Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,19,FWindsor and Lord Peter Mandelson's
OL,20,Flinks to Jeffrey Epstein.
