OL,3,CAustralian PM supports removing Andrew
OL,4,Cfrom royal line of succession
OL,6,FAsked about calls for a committee to
OL,7,Finvestigate the matter, the Prime
OL,8,FMinister's official spokesman said:
OL,9,F"This is a matter for Parliament, not
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,F"But we should remain mindful of the
OL,13,Fongoing investigation in this case,
OL,14,Fand it's right that the police
OL,15,Finvestigation takes its course."
OL,17,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,18,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,19,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,20,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
